  "name": "RPlog_An_Unexpected_Journey",
  "title": "An Unexpected Journey",
  "summary": "Aboard his freighter Arachnea, CDU Commander Adam Shadow wakes drugged to find a stowaway droid brain has hijacked his ship and diverted it to Nar Shaddaa, where the Twi'lek pirate Kora and her hired guns Sid and the Tusken Raider Sulla wait to capture him and steal the vessel. When Kora's remote fails to open the ship, Shadow seals the interior and fortifies a cabin, turning the boarding into a deadly trap. In the ensuing firefight he blinds the attackers with a flash grenade, drops Kora with a precise stun bolt, and dodges the enraged Sulla's gaffi-stick charge before stunning the Tusken into unconsciousness. With all three invaders subdued and bound, Shadow has his droid Clicker locate the stowaway droid brain, disconnects it, and finally sets course for Caspar with three captive prisoners in his hold.",
